'''''Twerps''''' is a [[shoot 'em up]] written by Dan Thompson for the [[Apple II]] and published by [[Sirius Software]] in 1982. It was ported to the [[Atari 8-bit computers]] by Joe Kelly.<ref name=giantlist/>

==Gameplay==
''Twerps'' is a game in which an explorer ship with its crew of nine Twerps crashed on an asteroid, and Captain Twerp must rescue the stranded Twerps.<ref name="CGW10"/>

==Reception==
